data.description: Huge Two Story Home - This property is a stucco two story home with an unfinished basement. The living room has a gas log fireplace and walkout dining room to large trex deck. Stay cool in the summer with air conditioning. The home has three bedrooms and two and one half baths with an unfinished basement for tons of extra storage. Enjoy your free time with a xeriscaped front yard and sprinkler system with fenced back yard. Two car attached garage. Close to Peterson AFB and Ft. Carson. This property is no pets and no smoking.. No Pets Allowed (RLNE5028802)
